# Student Performance Tracker

## Overview
This project demonstrates how Microsoft Excel can be used to manage, analyze, and visualize student academic performance efficiently.

The workbook includes features such as:
- Student data management
- Percentage calculation
- Automated grade assignment
- Pass/Fail evaluation
- Conditional formatting
- Pivot table analysis
- Data visualization

## Objectives
- Organize student performance data
- Automate calculations using Excel formulas
- Generate meaningful insights through analysis
- Present results using visual dashboards

## Tools Used
- Microsoft Excel
- Pivot Tables
- Conditional Formatting
- Charts and Visualizations
- Excel Formulas

